items.title: Awesome Malware Analysis
items.content_text:
### Memory Forensics / Other Resources

*   [Muninn (⭐52)](https://github.com/ytisf/muninn) - A script to automate portions
    of analysis using Volatility, and create a readable report.
    [Orochi (⭐246)](https://github.com/LDO-CERT/orochi) - Orochi is an open source framework for
    collaborative forensic memory dump analysis.
items.content_html:

  • Muninn (⭐52) - A script to automate portions of analysis using Volatility, and create a readable report. Orochi (⭐246) - Orochi is an open source framework for collaborative forensic memory dump analysis.
